collection.name: Magic Mushroom Clubhouse
collection.description: The Magic Mushroom Clubhouse is a friendly troop of 9,200 explorers scavenging the biotic metaverse. They earn badges on their adventures by spreading the ancient power of mushrooms, discovering the secrets of their ancestors and helping others along the way. Earn Celium points just for holding and redeem them for cool prizes including Whitelist spots, NFTS and more at https://mmcmarketplace.io/
